summary: story I want to share after seeing a lot of negativity about the hiatus
body:
story I want to share after seeing a lot of negativity about the hiatus

There was this indie band I really liked, who just like Dan and Phil, interacted with their fans a lot and had weekly live shows. However, this band stopped their weekly live shows and suddenly became silent on social media. Shortly after, all of their social media accounts were deactivated with no explanation. The members eventually created their own instagram account, but they never ever addressed what happened to the band. It hurts so much because they would always thank us for our support and remind us how much we mean to them. Yet, they just deleted everything and pretended as if this band never existed, while ignoring the presence of their fans. We all of course wanted a simple explanation from them, but that never happened.

I guess what I want to say is, yes Dan and Phil aren’t as active as they once were on social media, but hey, they still occasionally interact with us, and Phil is making videos. In addition, they did give us a heads up about the hiatus, but not as detailed as it could’ve been. So please continue to be patient with them because they have already done so much for us. Most importantly, they haven’t forgotten about us.

body:
small updates!


hey babycakes! i hope you all are enjoying this wonderful thursday morning/afternoon/night.

I am going to give you a few updates so then you guys won’t miss anything.

1. i have my own account!! it’s called @nepbanters it’s an account i made a switch to for a fresh start. this account has been turned into a fanfiction account so if you don’t want to read my hideous stories then you can definitely check out my other account!

2. I will be coming out with a fanfiction v soon. it’s called “Packing, Flirting and Multitasking.”

it’s a x fem!reader, and you’ll see who it is soon! also if you decide you wanna request a fanfiction please read the rules about requests and i’ll be happy to try and write some requests.

3. i am certainly going to be busy this summer. i have many things going on and i promise i’ll try to catch up on some fanfictions in my free time.

4. I will not be so active after my new fanfiction coming out, i have summer school all next week and also i have a recital coming up in a bit for dance. but i’ll try to write one when i’m in the dressing room (lol)

that is all i have right now. i’ll update you all real soon! have a fantastic weekend and i’ll see you soon.

peaches and cream

- nep
